line_1: With us the least desire of Respite scorns;
line_2: He with us sacred Nymphs profusely Mourns,

line_1: And man, that was his terror, scorns.
How Nobly Anthony the Empire scorns:

line_2: He quite forgot to add the horns.

line_1: And he's puff'd down, who their fine flams scorns,
line_2: Like Jericho, at blast of rams-horns.
